<td rowspan="4"><a href="/wiki/Academy_Awards" title="Academy Awards">Academy Awards</a></td>
<td><a href="/wiki/Academy_Award_for_Best_Sound_Editing" title="Academy Award for Best Sound Editing">Best Sound Editing</a></td>
