<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Theme_park_attraction">Theme park attraction</span></h2>
<p><a href="/wiki/Armageddon_%E2%80%93_Les_Effets_Speciaux" title="Armageddon – Les Effets Speciaux">Armageddon – Les Effets Speciaux</a> is an attraction based on <i>Armageddon</i> at <a href="/wiki/Walt_Disney_Studios_Park" title="Walt Disney Studios Park">Walt Disney Studios Park</a> located at <a href="/wiki/Disneyland_Paris" title="Disneyland Paris">Disneyland Paris</a>.<sup id="cite_ref-29" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-29"><span>[</span>29<span>]</span></a></sup> The attraction simulates the scene in the movie in which the Russian Space Station is destroyed.<sup id="cite_ref-photosmagiques1_30-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-photosmagiques1-30"><span>[</span>30<span>]</span></a></sup> <a href="/wiki/Michael_Clarke_Duncan" title="Michael Clarke Duncan">Michael Clarke Duncan</a> ("Bear" in the film) is featured in the pre-show.<sup id="cite_ref-photosmagiques1_30-1" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-photosmagiques1-30"><span>[</span>30<span>]</span></a></sup></p>
